# Supabase — use a NEW EMPTY project for a clean distribution (all nav counts 0).
# 1. Create a project at https://supabase.com (same schema: contacts table, etc.)
# 2. Copy this file to .env and set your project's URL and anon key below.
# 3. Run or build the app; it will use this project and start with 0 contacts.

SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
SUPABASE_KEY=your-anon-key-here
